"title": "5942: security",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5942",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Guaranteed safety, whether natural or spiritual, from danger or loss. Scripture stresses that ultimate security is to be found only in God himself.</p>\n<h2>The security of Israel</h2>\n<h3>Their security was found in God himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:27\">DEU 33:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:26\">DEU 33:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:28-Deut33:29\">DEU 33:28–33:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:21-Ezra8:23\">EZR 8:21–8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:10-Jer31:11\">JER 31:10–31:11</a></p>\n<h3>They were secure from danger and loss</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:17\">ISA 54:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:27-Ezek34:28\">EZK 34:27–34:28</a></p>\n<h3>Their security was conditional upon obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:6\">DEU 28:1–28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:19\">DEU 28:15–28:19</a></p>\n<h2>The security of believers is guaranteed</h2>\n<h3>By the everlasting covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:5\">2SA 23:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:29–8:30</a></p>\n<h3>In spiritual security in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">JHN 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:15\">JHN 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></p>\n<h3>In the provision of needs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5-Heb13:6\">HEB 13:5–13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:6-Ps118:7\">PSA 118:6–118:7</a></p>\n<h3>In safety from danger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1-Ps91:15\">PSA 91:1–91:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:3-Ps121:5\">PSA 121:3–121:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24-Jude1:25\">JUD 1:24–1:25</a></p>\n<h3>In a sure hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:27\">JOB 19:25–19:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:19\">HEB 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>In prophecies of security</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:21-Isa65:25\">ISA 65:21–65:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3-Mic4:4\">MIC 4:3–4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Provision for the security of human beings</h2>\n<h3>Protection for the weak</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:8-Ruth2:9\">RUT 2:8–2:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:1-1Sam11:6\">1SA 11:1–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:22-1Sam22:23\">1SA 22:22–22:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:6-Ezra6:7\">EZR 6:6–6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:29\">PRO 3:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:10\">ACT 23:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:23-Acts23:24\">ACT 23:23–23:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3\">ROM 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Financial pledges</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:1-Prov6:5\">PRO 6:1–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:15\">PRO 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:18\">PRO 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:26-Prov22:27\">PRO 22:26–22:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:35\">LUK 10:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:17-Phlm1:19\">PHM 1:17–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Pastoral protection</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:16\">JHN 21:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">ACT 20:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:19-Phil2:20\">PHP 2:19–2:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1-1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:1–5:2</a></p>\n<h2>False security</h2>\n<h3>In Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:21\">JER 22:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:17-Isa28:18\">ISA 28:17–28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13-Isa29:15\">ISA 29:13–29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:21-Dan11:24\">DAN 11:21–11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:1\">AMO 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:8\">LUK 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:33\">JHN 8:33</a></p>\n<h3>In the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:4\">REV 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14\">REV 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1-Rev3:2\">REV 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h3>In professing Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:12\">1CO 10:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:11-Matt22:12\">MAT 22:11–22:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:46\">MAT 25:41–25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9\">LUK 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:26-Heb10:27\">HEB 10:26–10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:21-2Pet2:22\">2PE 2:21–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8-1John1:10\">1JN 1:8–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:4\">JUD 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>In the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">1TH 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:11\">JDG 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:7\">JDG 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:3-1Sam24:4\">1SA 24:3–24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:6\">JOB 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:14\">JOB 18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24\">JOB 31:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:24\">PRO 27:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:15\">ZEC 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:28\">LUK 17:26–17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>",
